2026-03-04 08:02:27,081 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'number': 13, 'text': '## Goal\nReplace all legacy PNG icons and background images in the sa_jobman tree with Lucide icons and DaisyUI semantic color classes for full theme compatibility.\n\n## What changes\n\n### 1. Progress bar (CSS-only)\n- Remove `background-image: url("/img/ora-0.5.png")` and `url("/img/grn-0.5.png")`\n- Replace with `linear-gradient(var(--color-warning))` / `linear-gradient(var(--color-success))`\n- Replace `background-color: #eee` with `var(--color-base-200)`\n- JS `background-size: X% 100%` inline style stays unchanged\n\n### 2. Status icons — opnparts + NCR (JS formatter + CSS cleanup)\n- Formatter outputs `<span data-lucide="..." class="w-3.5 h-3.5 inline-block ml-1 text-warning">` spans\n- Tree plugin\'s existing `initIcons()` auto-converts after `loadData` — no plugin change needed\n- Icons: box/square-check (opnparts), triangle-alert (NCR)\n- Colors: text-warning (pending), text-success (done), text-error (open NCR)\n- No icons = no spans = no blank space (collapses naturally)\n- Remove all `.opnparts`, `.opnparts-closed`, `.ncr`, `.ncr.closed` CSS rules\n\n### 3. Node type icons (JS data + plugin tweak + CSS)\n- sa_jobman.js: change tree node `iconCls` from `bas/sub/seq/seq-C/seq-X/seq-U` to Lucide names (`folder/network/wrench/circle-check/x-circle/lock`) + add `iconColor` property (`text-primary/text-secondary/text-warning/text-success/text-error`)\n- tree-plugin.js: 2-line change — pass `nodeData.iconColor` to `$.dui.icon(cls, {color: nodeData.iconColor})` at lines ~85 and ~124\n- CSS: replace `.tree-icon.seq + .tree-title::before` selectors with `li.type-seq .tree-title::before` (using node `cls` property for type class)\n- Remove all `.tree-icon.bas/sub/seq/seq-*` PNG background rules\n\n### Files\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/css/sa_jobman.css` — remove PNG rules, theme-friendly progress bar, new ::before selectors\n- `html/dui/mod/vwltsa/js/sa_jobman.js` — iconCls/iconColor mapping, formatter status icons as data-lucide\n- `public/dui/js/plugins/tree-plugin.js` — pass iconColor to $.dui.icon() (2 lines)\n\n### Color mapping\n| Icon | Lucide | DaisyUI color |\n|------|--------|---------------|\n| Job folder | folder | text-primary |\n| Sub assembly | network | text-secondary |\n| Seq released | wrench | (base-content) |\n| Seq unreleased | lock | text-warning |\n| Seq closed | circle-check | text-success |\n| Seq cancelled | x-circle | text-error |\n| Parts to issue | box | text-warning |\n| Parts all issued | square-check | text-success |\n| NCR open | triangle-alert | text-error |\n| NCR closed | triangle-alert | text-success |'}
2026-03-04 08:04:32,274 807513 DEBUG mcpp.tool CALL plan_step_notes_set args={'id': 607, 'text': '## Goal\nReplace all legacy PNG icons and background images in the sa_jobman tree with fixed Lucide icons and theme-compatible DaisyUI color classes.\n\n**Icons are FIXED** — same icon regardless of theme.\n**Colors are THEME-COMPATIBLE** — DaisyUI semantic classes adapt to active theme.\n\n## Changes\n\n### 1. Progress bar (CSS-only)\n- Replace PNG background-images with CSS gradients using DaisyUI color vars\n- `background-color: #eee` → `var(--color-base-200)`\n- `ora-0.5.png` → `linear-gradient(var(--color-warning), var(--color-warning))`\n- `grn-0.5.png` → `linear-gradient(var(--color-success), var(--color-success))`\n- JS `background-size: X% 100%` inline style unchanged\n\n### 2. Status icons (JS formatter + CSS cleanup)\n- Formatter outputs `<span data-lucide="..." class="...">` — tree plugin\'s initIcons() auto-converts\n- No icons = no spans = no blank space\n- Remove all `.opnparts`, `.ncr` CSS rules\n\n### 3. Node type icons (JS data + 2-line plugin tweak + CSS)\n- Map iconCls to Lucide names + iconColor for DaisyUI color\n- tree-plugin.js: pass nodeData.iconColor to $.dui.icon() (2 lines)\n- CSS ::before prefixes: use li.type-seq/type-sub selectors\n- Remove all .tree-icon.bas/sub/seq PNG rules\n\n### Fixed icons + theme colors\n| Element | Lucide icon (fixed) | DaisyUI color (theme) |\n|---------|--------------------|-----------------------|\n| Job folder | folder | text-primary |\n| Sub assembly | network | text-secondary |\n| Seq released | wrench | (inherits base-content) |\n| Seq unreleased | lock | text-warning |\n| Seq closed | circle-check | text-success |\n| Seq cancelled | x-circle | text-error |\n| Parts to issue | box | text-warning |\n| Parts all issued | square-check | text-success |\n| NCR open | triangle-alert | text-error |\n| NCR closed | triangle-alert | text-success |\n| Progress bar (incomplete) | n/a | --color-warning fill, --color-base-200 bg |\n| Progress bar (complete) | n/a | --color-success fill |'}
